- Updated handle_alerts.py to use Firebase instead of MongoDB
- Updated exits.py to use Firebase for document operations
- Created migration script to transfer data from MongoDB to Firebase
- Created a test utility to verify Firebase connection
- Centralized collection name in env.py and updated all references

## Future Improvements
